sting lightweight approach\n- `#screenshotImage` cursor becomes `pointer` via CSS `.screenshot-image:not(.hidden)` — avoids cursor on hidden state\n- Lightbox `z-index: 100` — above `.app-header` z-index: 10 and command dropdown z-index: 100 (same layer, lightbox renders on top)\n- Lightbox closes on Esc — must check lightbox state before propagating to command dropdown handler\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] Task 1: Add lightbox HTML to index.html\n- [ ] Task 2: Add lightbox CSS to styles.css (including dark mode)\n- [ ] Task 3: Add lightbox JS to main.js (open/close/Esc)\n- [ ] Task 4: Add cursor:pointer to screenshot-image when visible\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":24,"oldLines":7,"newStart":24,"newLines":7,"lines":[" "," ## Tasks"," ","-- [ ] Task 1: Add lightbox HTML to index.html","-- [ ] Task 2: Add lightbox CSS to styles.css (including dark mode)","-- [ ] Task 3: Add lightbox JS to main.js (open/close/Esc)","-- [ ] Task 4: Add cursor:pointer to screenshot-image when visible","+- [x] Task 1: Add lightbox HTML to index.html","+- [x] Task 2: Add lightbox CSS to styles.css (including dark mode)","+- [x] Task 3: Add lightbox JS to main.js (open/close/Esc)","+- [x] Task 4: Add cursor:pointer to screenshot-image when visible"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
